videos.description: Temple's Mia Davis goes coast to coast and converts the layup in transition, earning a trip to the line for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Davis goes coast to coast for and-1 layup

videos.description: UConn's Megan Walker dishes the ball off to Gabby Williams in transition for the lay-in and chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Walker sets up Williams' and-1 layup

videos.description: Temple's Mia Davis takes it down the paint and sinks the tough layup, earning a trip to the line for a 3-point opportunity.
videos.headline: Davis converts tough lay-in for 3-point chance

videos.description: UConn's Megan Walker swings the ball over to Kia Nurse for the deep 3-pointer in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Nurse shows off the range on long 3

videos.description: UConn's Kia Nurse dishes the ball off to Gabby Williams in transition for the layup in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Huskies' nice ball movement leads to easy bucket

videos.description: UConn's Kia Nurse dishes the ball out to Gabby Williams, who passes back to Nurse for the easy lay-in.
videos.headline: Nurse converts give-and-go layup

videos.description: After hauling in the defensive rebound, UConn's Kia Nurse goes coast to coast and converts a layup in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Nurse sinks finger roll

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Temple's Mykia Jones pulls up from downtown and converts the long 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Jones shows off range on deep 3
